Air France KLM was down by 10.2% in early session trading, Getlink fell 5.7%, while French airports company ADP retreated by 4.8%. Shares in hotels company Accor fell by 4.4%. France said it would bar all people coming from the UK for 48 hours from Sunday night, including freight carriers, whether by road, air, sea or rail, amid alarm about a rapidly spreading new strain of coronavirus that has caused cases to soar in the UK. --Reuters--